headline.main: Eight-Year-Old Canadian Goalie's Dance Moves Go Viral
headline.print_headline: Eight-Year-Old Canadian Goalie's Dance Moves Go Viral

lead_paragraph: Costco Wholesale Corp. announced Thursday that it's raising its membership fees, as the warehouse club operator released quarterly results that fell short of Wall Street's expectations. Its shares fell more than 4 percent in after-hours trading.
